           #:lambda-match
           #:lambda-ematch
           #:lambda-cmatch
           #:lambda-match1
           #:lambda-ematch1
           #:lambda-cmatch1)
  (:documentation "
### [Pattern] alist

Syntax:

    (alist (KEY . PATTERN)*)

Expansion:

    (alist (k . p)*) => (and (assoc k p)*)

Examples:

    (match '((1 . :one) (2 . :two) (3 . :three))
      ((alist (1 . x) (3 . y)) (list x y)))
    => (:ONE :THREE)

### [Pattern] plist

Syntax:

    (plist {KEY PATTERN}*)

Expansion:

    (plist {k p}*) => (and (property k p)*)

Examples:

    (match '(:name \"John\" :age 23)
      ((plist :name \"John\" :age age) age))
    => 23"))
